      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PINCH OF SALT (7) failed to threaten on debut finishing seventh (19.03) at this track over 320m. Better for the run and makes appeal this time. ZIPPING JAKARA (3) held a forward position from the pinch but began to paddle on the bend and drifted out of the finish when 5th at this track in Maiden company. Worth another chance. ZIPPING BAFF (4) settled well back early on debut and always towards the tail to finish sixth (19.38) at this track over 320m. Can do far better this time. CRY TO ME (2) is by Tommy Shelby out of Utah Delta making debut. Drawn well and should get his chance. Profiles well so watch market closely.",
